  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/1444",
  "title": "How to set page parameter to start at 1 instead of 0? ",
  "body": "How do I set the trackedParameter for 'page' to start at 1 instead of 0?\n\nso that `/search?q=searchterm&page=0` is instead `/search?q=searchterm&page=1` on the first page?\n\nBasically I want to hook into the method that sets the querystring param, and just visually show it as +1 more than the actual page.\n\nThis could be an option using `urlSync`.\n",
